-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tam-Xuy%C3%AAn-quan-thu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-dYBU0BMWy96tMiL8Yl7EFA">Tam Xuyên quan thuỷ trướng nhị thập vận - 三川觀水漲二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Gia/T%E1%BA%B7ng-ph%E1%BB%A5-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-xOZqUA3BgbR8fD4Y1lVf9A">Tặng phụ thi kỳ 3 - 贈婦詩其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Gia/author-djGByRNyyXxtcykD8j_JTA">Tần Gia</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-Thi%C3%AAn-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-v%E1%BB%87-u%C3%BD-h%E1%BB%93i-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-Tv0AVCahP49b2Ya8--Ck3Q">Tiễn Thiên Trường vệ uý hồi hương - 餞天長衛尉回鄉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/T%C3%ADn/poem-mg0J7wkm3ti0EQ-2RTuZ6g">Tín - 信</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
